Module com.malvi

Package p4_group_8_repo

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Actor
    Actor is an ImageView.
    BackgroundImage
    This class sets the background for the game play.
    Digit
    This class holds objects of the numbers displayed for the score.
    End
    This class represents the players home, which is at the top of the screen.
    GetImageFromSpriteSheet
    This class reads pixels of a spritesheet and uses the colours of these pixels to extract single frames of images.
    Highscore
    This class handles reading and writing the highest score to a text file.
    ImageLoader
    This class loads all the images into the game prior to starting game play.
    Log
    This method is responsible for the log objects.
    Main
    Main class has the single responsibility of changing scenes.
    MyStage
    This is a Concrete class of the game World.
    Player
    This singleton class represents the player.
    SpriteAnimation
    This class is used to set animations for the turtles.
    Turtle
    This class is responsible for the creation of the Red Turtles.
    Vehicle
    This class is responsible for instantiating all Vehicle objects.
    WetTurtle
    This class is responsible for the green turtles which can sink inside the water.
    World
    World class is a custom JavaFX control.
